                            <a href="#" class="block tracking-wide uppercase sm:normal-case text-3xl md:text-base py-5 pr-4 pl-3 text-gray-700 border-b border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50 lg:hover:bg-transparent lg:border-0 lg:hover:text-yellow-700 lg:p-0 lg:">Rates</a>
